OL,3,CPlant disease which causes fruit to
OL,4,Cshrivel spreads across Jersey
OL,6,FA serious plant disease which kills
OL,7,Ffruit blossoms and hedges by starving
OL,8,Fthem of water has been found spreading
OL,9,Facross Jersey with 66 cases confirmed
OL,10,Fso far.
OL,12,FFireblight causes the blossoms of the
OL,13,Ffruits to darken and makes twigs,
OL,14,Fflowers and leaves look as though they
OL,15,Fhave been burned by fire.
OL,17,FWhile officials believe it may now be
OL,18,Ftoo prevalent to eradicate in the
OL,19,Fisland, they hope the spread can be
OL,20,Fmanaged.
