OL,3,CPlant disease which causes fruit to
OL,4,Cshrivel spreads across Jersey
OL,6,FThere is no known risk to humans but
OL,7,Fthe disease can devastate crop yields.
OL,9,FInsects, including pollinators such as
OL,10,Fbees, can carry the harmful bacteria
OL,11,Fto the flowers of other healthy plants.
OL,13,FThe Head Winemaker at Le Mare Estate,
OL,14,FJordi Sanvicens Moreno, says that
OL,15,Faround 30% of his apple orchard was
OL,16,Finfected by the disease which lead to
OL,17,Fthe loss of the entire crop.
OL,19,FThe Government's Environmental
OL,20,FDepartment has been worrking to
OL,21,Fprotect the remaining healthy plants.
