OL,4,Cshrivel spreads across Jersey
OL,6,FPlant Pathologist Steve Thompson
OL,7,Fexplains: "Fireblight is a bacterial
OL,8,Fdisease which affects plants from the
OL,9,FRosacae family.
OL,11,F"It originally started in North
OL,12,FAmerica, it's probably been in Europe
OL,13,Ffor the last 50 to 100 years, and we
OL,14,Fhave a big problem.
OL,16,F"Years ago, the policy was you would
OL,17,Feradicate the disease by cutting back
OL,18,Fand grubbing out hedges and so forth.
